verbose_text: Content of SOD2 has increased in the livers of mice fed a ketogenic diet (% energy : 89 fat, < 1 carbohydrate, and 10 protein), which occurred in conjunction with increased median lifespan and decreases in tumors and age associated losses of physical and cognitive performance [XREF_BIBR].
